## Task 3: Basic Chatbot

### Objective
Build a simple rule-based chatbot that responds to predefined user inputs.

### Features
- Greets the user
- Responds to common questions
- Ends the conversation when the user types "bye" or "exit"

### Concepts Used
- Functions
- if-elif statements
- while loop
- Input and Output

